Dialogue: 9,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Qual é aquela espada?!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:50.51,0:13:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Cortou tanto o placenta quanto o núcleo!{japanese katana, cutting even alien ultra stuff}
Dialogue: 9,0:13:53.89,0:13:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Poxa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:19.99,100 Sights,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}100 Atrações de Sidonia
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:16.99,100 Sights - Copy,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Strato 4721, Bairro Comercial Oriental
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:19.99,100 Sights - Copy,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Sala de Manutenção Híbrida
Dialogue: 9,0:14:20.50,0:14:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Recuperamos o contato com Tanikaze.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:22.88,0:14:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Todos estão bem.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:26.26,0:14:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Novo contato com Gauna vindo \das nuvens de gás.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:30.84,0:14:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:31.64,0:14:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Elimine aquele Gauna \e encontre-se com Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:35.18,0:14:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:37.52,0:14:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Acho que a Espada Gaunabane \perdeu muito do seu afiamento nessa primeira cortada.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:45.23,0:14:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Está tudo bem.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Podemos ainda melhorar.{improve it? this sounds weird in this context}
Dialogue: 9,0:14:51.91,0:14:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0]...[T1]Tsumugi...
Dialogue: 9,0:15:55.76,0:15:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Peço desculpas.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:57.97,0:16:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Queria que todos os seus placentas fossem levados embora.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:07.82,0:16:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Vou penetrar no seu núcleo agora.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:38.14,0:16:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugi!
Dialogue: 9,0:16:38.93,0:16:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Se afaste de Benisuzume!
