Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:36.33,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Se este mundo estiver condenado à destruição,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:36.33,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}se kuchiteku sekai naraba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:39.83,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Se minha vida estiver em jogo,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:39.83,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}se eu tiver que morrer,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:45.42,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}então por que viveria?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:45.42,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}não saberia o que crer para viver
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:51.09,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Se não tivesse conhecido você,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:51.09,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}se eu nunca tivesse te encontrado
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.09,0:22:54.51,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}então eu nunca sentiria dor assim
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.09,0:22:54.51,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}como se meu coração fosse arrancado
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.68,0:23:01.10,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}quebrando meu coração
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.68,0:23:01.10,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}por não conhecer dor
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.56,0:23:03.86,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}é um requiem primitivo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.56,0:23:03.86,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}no horizonte do céu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:05.32,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}ecoando até
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:05.32,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}ressoou nas noites
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:09.15,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}as extensões do céu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:09.15,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}um requiem inexpressivo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.15,0:23:11.07,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}E até agora
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.15,0:23:11.07,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}ainda assim muito
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:12.78,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}em esse mundo sem sentido
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:12.78,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]sagashiteiru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.82,0:23:16.20,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}eu busco
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.82,0:23:16.20,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}diferente desde agora
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.20,0:23:18.16,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}por ti
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.20,0:23:18.16,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}o que te diz
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.16,0:23:21.83,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,1. {\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Lembro
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.16,0:23:21.83,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,2. {\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}da alegria de te conhecer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:25.55,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,3. {\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e o prazer da sua presença
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:25.55,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,4. {\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}tudo que sinto é recordação
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:29.76,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,5. {\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}porque eu te amava
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:29.76,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]nee zenbu oboeteru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.76,0:23:32.84,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]porque eu te amava
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.76,0:23:32.84,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]aishiteta kara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.84,0:23:36.60,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Gelo se forma no meu coração
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.84,0:23:36.60,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}mesmo o mapa do mar congelado
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.60,0:23:40.31,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}sobre as feridas dentro de mim
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.60,0:23:40.31,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}as cicatrizes que permanecem no peito
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:44.69,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}eu levarei tudo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:44.69,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e carregarei tudo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.69,0:23:51.70,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e caminharei pelo meu caminho
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.69,0:23:51.70,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}eu caminharei por esta estrada
